{"word":"ἐκεῖθεν","slug":"ἐκεῖθεν","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐκεῖθεν</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:ἐκεῖ'><el>ἐκεῖ</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>from that place, thence</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>illinc</el>, <a href='S:opposed to'>opp. to</a> <el>ἐκεῖσε</el>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>= <a href='S:ἐκεῖ'><el>ἐκεῖ</el></a>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>:—<a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <el>τοὐκεῖθεν ἄλσους</el> on <i>yon</i> side of the grove, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>thence, from that fact</i>, <b><a href='S:Isocrates'>Isocr.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b>of Time, <i>thereafter, next</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}